quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Taa Siin, …óeen ko aayeeje Alqur'aanaare nden e deftere …ďanngunde."
  27,2,"Ko nde Peewal e welo-welo wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  27,3,"∆Āeen …ďe no √Īii…ďa e Juulde nden …ďe totta askal on, kam…ďe he…ďe njananaa fii Laakara on."
  27,4,"Pellet, …ďeen …ďe ngooŇč…óinaani Laakara on, Min cu…óanii …ďe golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, kam…ďe he…ďe mbumo."
  27,5,"Ko …ďeen ngoni …ďen, …ďe woodani …óum Lepte bon…óe …óen, kam…ďe ka Laakara ko kam…ďe ngoni hayru…ďe …ďeen."
  27,6,"E pellet, an ha…óa lonnginee Alqur'aanaare nden immorde ka √Ďee√Īo ganndu…óo."
  27,7,"Tuma nde Muusaa maakannoo …ďeynguure makko nden: "Min dey, mi haynike yiite, mi addana on ka nge woni …óon kumpital ma mi addana on docotal ku…ď…ďungal, bela jo'o onon on itwoto."
  27,8,"Tuma nde o arnoo e magge, o noddaa: ∆äuum woni barkinaama on won…óo ka yiite e …ďen won…ďe banŇče magge, e Senaare wonanii Alla Jooma winndere nden."
  27,9,"Eey ma Muusaa, ko woni, ko Min woni Alla Teddu…óo √Ďee√Ī…óo On."
  27,10,"Li…ďu tuggordu maa…óa ndun, Tuma nde o yi'unoo ndu hundu dilla, a wi'ayma kayru ko ndu mboo…ódi, o hucciti ko o dogu…óo o yiltitaake. Ko an yo Muusaa: "Wata a hul, Min dey Nulaa…ďe …ďen kulataa to Am"."
  27,11,"Si wonaa oon too√Ī…óo, refti o lomtini ko mo∆ī∆īi …ďaawo bone …óen. Pellet, Min ko Mi cuhroowo Jurmetee…óo."
  27,12,"Naatnu junngo ma ngon ka jiiba maa…óa, ngo yaltay ko ngo ranewo ko aldaa e bone, […óum no jeyaa] e ndeer aayeeje jeenay nulaa…óe e Fir'awna e yim…ďe makko …ďen, pellet, kam…ďe …ďe laatike yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe."
  27,13,"Tuma nde arnoo e ma…ď…ďe Aayeeje amen …óen ko yi'etee…óe, …ďe mbi'i: "∆äu'um, ko mbilewu …ďanngungu"."